    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Waxwing</strong> 是一款合作 2D 横向卷轴飞行游戏，你和你的搭档可以发射吸引火焰，引导英雄完成一系列惊险挑战——但小心不要太靠近火焰。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>影响，而非控制</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328210/extras/3c83e2f97ab8c1105cda855cbd388c7c.poster.avif?t=1758503135\" width=800 height=442 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328210/extras/3c83e2f97ab8c1105cda855cbd388c7c.webm?t=1758503135\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328210/extras/3c83e2f97ab8c1105cda855cbd388c7c.mp4?t=1758503135\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Waxwing 拥有独特的移动机制——你和你的搭档并非英雄本身，而是引导他们的力量。发射火焰来创建路标，引导英雄穿越关卡并避开途中的障碍物。但要小心——如果他们真的触碰到火焰，就会立即死亡，关卡也会自动重置。在短小、快节奏的关卡中，与你的搭档建立起来回的射击节奏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>追寻太阳，跨越人生</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328210/extras/f2f551f455252012882816fbcac9760f.poster.avif?t=1758503135\" width=800 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328210/extras/f2f551f455252012882816fbcac9760f.webm?t=1758503135\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328210/extras/f2f551f455252012882816fbcac9760f.mp4?t=1758503135\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验英雄的四段人生，每段人生都有各自的主题、艺术和敌人。带领英雄穿过蜘蛛网、咆哮的青少年和黑洞。收集星星，直面太阳。一个失误，你就死定了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>经典元素的全新演绎</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328210/extras/77b9a73384b4692015573eeea278a237.poster.avif?t=1758503135\" width=800 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328210/extras/77b9a73384b4692015573eeea278a237.webm?t=1758503135\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328210/extras/77b9a73384b4692015573eeea278a237.mp4?t=1758503135\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Waxwing 融合了各种意想不到的游戏元素——精准平台游戏的狭窄走廊和快速重生、弹幕射击游戏的躲避动作、无尽奔跑的持续运动，甚至还有类似电脑角色扮演游戏 (CRPG) 和即时战略游戏 (RTS) 的“点击移动”控制模式——从而以出人意料的直观视角，展现挑战、移动和合作的全新视角。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>附言：——亲临现场体验</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >纽约布鲁克林 Wonderville 的 Waxwing 永久街机游戏机柜配备定制光枪控制器！</p>",
